Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:01:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Cruel Duel:\NYugi VS Jounouchi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two should be on their way shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To save their precious friends, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi and this girl have become my pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm looking forward to the show that's about to unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you, Rishid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you ordered, I have secured 12 Puzzle Cards for the Battle City Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took on enough Battle City Duels for two, and won every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that Trap Strategy of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to take control of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know you'd never betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... please accept these Puzzle Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm qualified to enter the Battle City Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid, along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Jounouchi the Deck of 40 cards we've prepared for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Jounouchi's deck has been transformed into a Banned Deck that can be used to assassin a player.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come for you to feel the furry of our clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the hands of your dear friend, you'll be sent to another world, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}... Please be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he truly has the power to control people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Malik probably already turned Jounouchi into a wild animal with its fangs drawn at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were him, that's what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! I don't know what he's up to, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it means saving Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gladly put my life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm already aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a serious self-contradiction 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you decided to follow that self-righteous path you're always preaching about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-contradiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our Tag Duel with those Rare Hunters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you showed me the power of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we don't combine our power in this Duel, we have no chance of defeating the Ghouls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you and Jounouchi are forced to fight one another this time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me where this "power of cooperation" lies {\i1}then{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Answer me{\i0}, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone down there! Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill him! KILL HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! The answer lies right ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you to show up, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he really {\b0}is{\b1} being controlled by Malik...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... Almost seems like a different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Malik's power of controlling people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! You've got to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wake up{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}wide{\i0} awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more than awake enough to beat you to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use...! His mind's being completely controlled by Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You can't run away from me or this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duel with our very lives on the line, fighting till our last breaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, just what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duelist must be prepared to crush all challengers 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,standing before them, even if they're his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the way of a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go against it, you'll never get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way... of a Duelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only way he'll win is if he tosses his usual "friendship"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sentimentality garbage aside, and just fights him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is one matchup that may be too much for Yugi to handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, what'll you do, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Show me your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to Duel you in Battle City from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as {\i1}True{\i0} Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our {\i1}pride{\i0} on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, when I win this tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when the time comes where I can call myself a True Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When that time comes, please fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the reason we've gotten this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was so I could keep that promise with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this battle is a {\i1}trap{\i0} set by Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the {\i1}true{\i0} Duel we promised each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage for our Duel of Death is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter {\b0}what{\b1} you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you can't escape this Duel with Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi has become my {\b0}puppet{\b1},
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his emotions and memory are being controlled by my anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu's under his spell, too...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi is waiting for you at the stage of your Death Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi is waiting for you at the stage of your Death Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our Duel stage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before the Duel begins, you will each attach these handcuffs to your ankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...! Mine and Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s handcuffs are attached to an anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The anchor weighs 300 kilograms [600 pounds]!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When either of the player's Life Points drop to 0,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bomb will explode within 30 seconds, and it will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And take a look at your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That box shows your opponent's Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to your handcuffs lies inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The box will open when you take your opponent's Life Points down to 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the anchor drags us to our watery graves, one of us can escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the loser of this Duel will be dragged to his death...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either me or you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can have such a dangerous Duel with Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The explosive device attached to the anchor has just been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you do nothing, it'll explode in 40 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that scenario, you'll {\b0}both{\b1} sink into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's very {\b0}simple{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you wish to save Jounouchi, all you need to do is {\b0}lose{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik! I'll {\i1}never{\i0} forgive you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A death match between Yugi and Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To make them fight such a sick Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just for Malik's {\b0}stupid{\b1} talk of "revenge for 3,000 years of torment"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's {\b0}seriously{\b1} trying to kill Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop them, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't accept this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a battle where no matter what they do, one of them dies...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't even a {\b0}Duel{\b1} anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will {\i1}not{\i0} let Malik do what he wants in this Battle City!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a bomb set up atop this container.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try anything and I'll press this switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dropping the container right on top of that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he'd go {\i1}this{\i0} low...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}, I'd love it if you could behave yourself and just watch 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as the {\b0}greatest{\b1} show in existence begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like for this {\b0}girl{\b1} to see this amazing show as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck {\i1}is{\i0} this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really dirty, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Anzu go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't even {\i1}close{\i0} to the suffering my clan and I have endured!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer more and more, Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then {\i1}die{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I almost forgot about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I could care less if {\i1}you{\i0} drown in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you better not take the Osiris card along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take Osiris out of your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep the God Card in {\i1}here{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red-Eyes Black Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now I can't take Red-Eyes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way I am now, Red-Eyes wouldn't {\i1}let{\i0} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So anyway, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll leave that card with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got no choice but to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I put his Red-Eyes in my deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use it to regain Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s Duelist heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the Osiris card on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So only the one who {\i1}lives{\i0} gets their hands on the God Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everything is in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassinate Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuffle your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here now, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It sure is nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This town's smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My big brother and I always came here when we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry up and see my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's {\i1}my{\i0} turn to give {\i1}him{\i0} courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's hurry and find Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay... I wonder where the guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is Anzu doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you get to go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...knowing one of us will die when our Life hits 0?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a sadistic Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey c'mon! What's wrong, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and play a Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion Beast King Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn... over...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Bolt!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play Wyvern Warrior on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Directly attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's {\i1}wrong{\i0}, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not so tough after all, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's way too early to start fearing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now bring it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Shield Gardna in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use pulling out a Wall Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use {\i1}this{\i0} against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Cards that directly damage the player are {\i1}banned{\i0} from this tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I added tons of illegal cards printed by the Ghouls to Jounouchi's deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one using a {\i1}store-made{\i0} deck can hope to beat {\i1}his{\i0} deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're about to be burnt to death by your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Die, hateful Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik, I just learned that Yugi's friend has brought Jounouchi's little sister to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's {\i1}little sister{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could be of great use to my avenging of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring her to me at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the illegal player assaulting banned card, Fireball, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill{\i0} your friend, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a puppet, a vessel of my desire for revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really don't want to fight you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the Duel we wished for...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s Duelist heart still hasn't disappeared from within him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}your{\i0} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}will{\b1} call it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your Duelist's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Card draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've asked where we were meeting {\i1}before{\i0} I left...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know my brother's somewhere in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure the others are as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry, we'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are {\i1}you{\i0} guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are Ghouls, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit... I'd have no trouble kicking their asses...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But protecting Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1} comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, climb on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you {\i1}doing{\i0}, Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me Jounouchi joined up with the Ghouls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... seems to be under the control of this Malik guy in charge of the Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under Malik's control?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's avenging his clan for 3,000 years of suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't get any of it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge for 3,000 years of suffering...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a battle related to the other Yugi and his lost memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a fuss over there, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep runnin' your mouth and I'm gonna send that container right down on ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can do it, why don't you go and {\i1}try it{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Jounouchi and Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what happens, you've got to endure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang on to your pride through this dishonorable Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come {\i1}on{\i0} now, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna buy time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put out a Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} has Wyvern Warrior with 1500 Attack Points on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I have Big Shield Gardna with 2600 Defense Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I don't have any cards right now strong enough to fight the Wyvern Warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have to strengthen my defense and try and buy some more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Kuriboh to the field in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kuriboh{\i0} in {\i1}Attack{\i0} Position?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}kidding{\i0} me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my Wyvern attacks your Kuriboh, 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, your Life Points are gonna take a serious hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So to save {\i1}my{\i0} life, {\i1}you're{\i0} gonna die instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't let {\i1}you{\i0} die either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel only ends {\i1}when{\i0} one of us dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyvern Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh is shielded by the Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Hexagram Curse stops the Wyvern Warrior from attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no use, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work against his Banned Deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether I play a Monster or {\i1}not{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do is drain your Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...eat {\i1}this{\i0} once again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIREBALL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(135,137)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Jounouchi still isn't waking up from Malik's control,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the other Yugi allows Yugi to take over the Duel in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing in their friendship, he Summons the Red-Eyes to remind Jounouchi of their bond together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring back Jounouchi's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take It Back! The Red-Eyes Black Dragon of Friendship"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here, always...
